gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d040be17c36de6a51ba36da05f60966e48a29972","tid":263892,"uid":29708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無知一問<br />\n點解會消化不良？</blockquote><br />\n容易食會無咬爛啲米就吞落<span style=\"font-size: large;\">肚</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我都唔明點解會消化不良<br />\n但係我覺得有湯啲飯反而會散開易咬啲<br />\n而且啲湯會浸淋少少啲飯<br />\n從來都未試過湯撈飯之後會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdb19b89d477e2538d68e51e566f9978b09452b","tid":263892,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"鍾意田七湯撈 苦苦地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2de43e74b0e5fd9a27f4e1e5981f28ffb3ed02","tid":263892,"uid":56360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"九紀湯撈飯超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec300d6b1d0a691c307905421fd90d0a7bbf9de2","tid":263892,"uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"咩湯都撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連忌廉湯都撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82d1a900704df837526b7c934e2d75126d78f8a","tid":263892,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"魚湯飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6404c4c6865c21b7fdb62268987de6f8a74a60b","tid":263892,"uid":102300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蕃茄薯仔魚湯飯"},{"pid":"0d1ff8ebf378ff98d0163ea716d6adc8b9d5569a","tid":263892,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":