" /><br />\n一睇到post已經想食咸菜豬肚湯撈飯<br />\n但食多兩餐真係會胃痛，食得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721fe8d27ba0de095aaea15b5112cffe93321a89","tid":263892,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"蘑菇薯仔忌廉湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b362c7b253b2c7ce9c48f019c41f11619a4636","tid":263892,"uid":73762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:14:04.000Z","msg":"細個成日撈 而家大個左個胃好差"},{"pid":"8473756e1aea3b612787c68d0a66ca00111a057a","tid":263892,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e11764ff4fa49457bcb83435317e0abd0a305859","tid":263892,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"會胃痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e3a02d588c34db844a527bbeab67cc4522d788","tid":263892,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"魚脣邊撈飯 有翅湯既味道<br />\n叉燒既價錢燒鵝既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d7b144af9c2e10f1afce548e60c41a9839d1ed","tid":263892,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"蕃茄薯仔湯配飯世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e458a4e28f398c67aea650132bf9b50bcb1cf27","tid":263892,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"要睇乜嘢湯<br />\n我細個好大食，食栗米羹撈飯我撈到接近半煲湯同埋2/3煲飯都冇埋，食到就嚟嘔為止，我老母老竇仲鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06917c5225d40c8aeda251ab7a390ab555bf1b4","tid":263892,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n中湯定西湯撈都正<br />\n<br />\nBtw 忌廉湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56790ed86155bdd852fe3ee78c3e89d1cecfe63","tid":263892,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蕃茄薯仔湯配飯世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粟米羹同埋番茄薯仔糖係我細個最鍾意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6f9e78c719efc1dd03efc0d222364d613d7b6d","tid":263892,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765d2dbcf81f979b9fe6bd18b34cb0591c6a243f","tid":263892,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"蕃茄薯仔湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 金寶湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4779a87eb3597cc9ca0689388806a1fb876c3027","tid":263892,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"其實落到胃唔係一樣咩？<br />\n如果咀嚼多幾口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6a6d437d1ff27f398f78c73014a1527771c04a","tid":263892,"uid":100393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"以前成日粟米湯撈飯跟住俾老母屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e345b3ea6ebd487b02dd92a6d376d61d0e82cfa3","tid":263892,"uid":119850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問<br />\n點解會消化不良？</blockquote><br />\n想問+1"},{"pid":"416ffce5746fb61aa858e91b22c1c8fb2f9fe7bc","tid":263892,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蕃茄薯仔湯配飯世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粟米羹同埋番茄薯仔糖係我細個最鍾意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呀媽唔俾咁食<br />\n而家食完飯先有湯飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d225766eff2974bd2a2d7563e82a55a0b989b5d7","tid":263892,"uid":45931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc74ca7989cb4dbb2eb5ca07fd3a250fc1635a9","tid":263892,"uid":5393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"勁鐘意 咩中湯都撈"},{"pid":"e45bb31fcf8f84d7676baf3b1573a4c65fdc37c9","tid":263892,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蕃茄薯仔湯配飯世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粟米羹同埋番茄薯仔糖係我細個最鍾意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呀媽唔俾咁食<br />\n而家食完飯先有湯飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粟米羹都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa2ad4883a1a98fb2cf9d119521b063cb883d95","tid":263892,"uid":21679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱撈完青紅蘿蔔雞腳湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時係嫌街啲飯太硬就會用湯撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e64a943cf77de2a6bc3acbbb2c9f5f6b8b03acf","tid":263892,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:33:02.000Z","msg":"不過有樣野唔明 如果啲飯落胃前咬多兩淡咬碎啲<br />\n咁仲會唔會消化不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係本身邊飲湯邊食飯會導致消化不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲湯同飯落到個胃都攪埋一齊消化嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69433495de2e5f1affe302164b469421cf494fc","tid":263892,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蕃茄薯仔湯配飯世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粟米羹同埋番茄薯仔糖係我細個最鍾意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呀媽唔俾咁食<br />\n而家食完飯先有湯飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲湯渣當埋飯餸咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b317cb3fa751ba20a7c7a05bc51c380d7bfcffe2","tid":263892,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我撈果陣唔會咁多湯<br />\n大約啱啱過到飯面左右就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:頭先晚飯啊媽煲左湯<br />\n撈左,勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n湯同飯個比例好緊要</blockquote><br />\n飯唔可以太淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d528e4630bae82550e0bd9a234c6a3b8c002d58","tid":263892,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實落到胃唔係一樣咩？<br />\n如果咀嚼多幾口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eec30a15077edb237fe33d1bc2d93d0ca6987a","tid":263892,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"255a4c3c27cf275c5e3138e7603fde2c6827038c","tid":263892,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"以前吉野家有個野菌泡飯好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我又鍾意食菇又鍾意食湯飯 次次食吉野家都叫 但後尾冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩之後出咗個關東煮泡飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然冇野菌泡飯咁正"},{"pid":"8ec47553e585f864d094965bcc156bef47ff3c42","tid":263892,"uid":36951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蕃茄薯仔魚湯飯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5386432c8dddd55fde9dbb0f2d5542782512a5","tid":263892,"uid":114235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無知一問<br />\n點解會消化不良？</blockquote><br />\n容易食會無咬爛啲米就吞落<span style=\"font-size: large;\">肚</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我都唔明點解會消化不良<br />\n但係我覺得有湯啲飯反而會散開易咬啲<br />\n而且啲湯會浸淋少少啲飯<br />\n從來都未試過湯撈飯之後會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問我老豆<br />\n佢話因為咁樣會沖淡胃酸，消化唔到飯粒<br />\n反而就咁食飯，飯粒會易啲消化<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> errrrrrr......<br />\n<br />\n利申: 老豆一介莽夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6018c68033081bd69a80d0eaea1a7823e77e2bca","tid":263892,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"